title: Environmental data from aquaculture
text:
Data collected from aquaculture locations throughout Washington. Data displayed here has not been quality controlled. Demonstration website.


Click each location on this map to find a list of the data that has been collected at each site and the organisation that has collected this data. Can easily add more sites by adding rows to a CSV file.




















Note that these daily averages include time that individuals were out of the water at low tide sites.






Github page created by Craig Norrie. Last updated 4 May 2024. This could be a location to have data hosted from multiple projects.

title: Thorndyke Bay environmental data
text:
Temperature data
Temperature data was collected from hobo DO and temp logger. Data was collected every 15 minutes and daily averages were calculated. Note this data included information from when individuals were out of the water. 
We can include additional lines with differtent colours for each of the locations within thorndyke to compare.

title: Thorndyke Bay environmental data
text:

Dissolved oxygen data was collected using a hobo DO and temp logger. Data was collected every 15 minutes and daily averages were calculated. Note this data included information from when individuals were out of the water
